Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬丁·吉連要求見你  事實上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martin Killane has asked to see you. In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只肯跟你說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he will only talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久以前做了件很壞的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did a terrible thing a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始做必須要做的事之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And before what has to happen begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你說說這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我只信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're the only person I trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能理解嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你見過我妻子的照片  娜塔莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've seen photos of my wife, Natasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她出現時  我以為我是這世上最幸運的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I was the luckiest man alive when she came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是那么美麗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was so gorgeous and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有挑戰性  對我要求很高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}challenging and demanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她顛覆了我的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She turned my world upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我崇拜她  我非常崇拜她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I adored her, I completely adored her.
