Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}attention, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我是個整天忙碌的警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a cop working all hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她去找其他男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So she meets other men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "夠了  我受夠了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I say, "That's it, that's it." And...
