Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們生個孩子吧"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's have a baby."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we do.
