Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子改變了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this baby changes everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都沉迷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm besotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總處于一種難以置信的狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm in a constant state of amazement.
